      "span_text": "As described previously  , the FTIR data were collected using a Hyperion 3000 FTIR imaging system (Bruker Optics, Ettlingen, Germany), equipped with a 64*64 Mercury Cadmium Telluride (MCT) Focal Plane Array (FPA) detector."
